title: Inspector Rex S2 Ep26 - Children On The Run
description:
Inspector Rex S2 Ep26 - Children On The Run

Children on the Run - Horst Bacher, a heavy drinker, is sent home from work for being drunk on the job. When he gets home, he argues with his wife and ends up killing her and kidnapping their two children. Will Brandtner and Rex be able to rescue the children before more harm is done? Stars Gedeon Burkhard, Heinz Weixelbraun and Martin Weinek. 

From Austria, in German

Subtitles by SBS AU TV
